Guidelines for comprehensive exuality education. (n.d.) Guidelines. Retrieved on September 10, 2004 from http://www.siecus.org/school/sex_ed/guidelines/guide0000.html

Humboldt University. Mangus Hirschfeld Archive of Sexology (n.d.) Retrieved September 10 from http://www2.hu-berlin.de/sexology/index.html

Mackay, J. (2000). Global Sex: Sexuality and sexual practices around the world. 5th Congress of the European Federation of Sexology. Berlin, Germany.




